summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire land and other property in Block 23, H. L. yesler's 1st Addition to the City of Seattle for the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project, as provided in Ordinance 104086, King County Cause No. 799782; accepting the condemnation award in connection therewith; and authorizing expenditures from the Project Expenditure Fund, WASH R-5 therefor.
